snippet.title: Tempest - Pirate City DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
More details can be found here: http://bit.ly/piratecity

Develop your own city and fight off pirate zombies in the upcoming DLC for Tempest - an Open World Action RPG where you rove the seas across three continents filled with dozens of colonies and forts, hundreds of quests and countless ships to plunder. Customize your ship, trade, challenge fellow pirates and face terrible mythical monsters such as Kraken and Leviathan.
